        "desc": "<p>仙人是一群生活在提瓦特的不朽之物，千年來一直保護著璃月的人們。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/7372a2d1b47769b64d0e87bd21a867a7_1916279790302197166.png",
